# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OEDON -- Declarative Application Registry (apps.list)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Format: name | internal-port | subdomain
#
# The full domain is built at deploy time: {subdomain}.{DOMAIN}
# DOMAIN is read from .env (e.g., DOMAIN=hello.test -> static.hello.test)
#
# Rules:
#   - "name" must match the container_name in its docker-compose.yml
#   - "port" is the INTERNAL port inside oedon-network
#   - "subdomain" is the prefix only (no dots, no full domain)
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Name             | Port  | Subdomain
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
oedon-static      | 80     | static
wordpress         | 9000   | wordpress
python-app        | 5000   | python

# Examples (uncomment when deployed):
# moodle          | 8080   | lms
# gitea           | 3000   | git
# pulse           | 8080   | gestion
